---
/**
 * WhyChris — text-only section. Orange headline + three short paragraphs.
 * Copy verbatim from bundle (Chris's lines).
 */
---

<section class="cc-why">
  <div class="cc-why-inner">
    <h2 class="cc-why-headline">Why Chris</h2>
    <div class="cc-why-body">
      <p>
        Most people in this space help companies use tools better. I help you rethink what those tools are sitting on.
      </p>
      <p>
        I&rsquo;m not here to optimize broken processes, set up software in isolation, or automate what isn&rsquo;t working.
      </p>
      <p>
        I help you step back, see the bigger pattern, and rebuild how your business actually works, so your people and AI can create value together.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cc-why {
    padding: 60px clamp(24px, 20vw, 390px);
  }
  .cc-why-inner {
    max-width: 910px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 40px;
  }
  .cc-why-headline {
    font-family: var(--cc-font-display);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4.2vw, 64px);
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--cc-mirinda);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .cc-why-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
    font-family: var(--cc-font-body);
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--cc-pearl);
  }
  .cc-why-body p {
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
